# Data and Artifacts (except the ones we explicitly copy)
# We ignore the entire models/ and data/ folder initially,
# BUT we explicitly COPY them in the Dockerfile.
# Wait, actually Dockerfile COPY models/ ./models/ will respect .dockerignore!
# If we ignore models/ in .dockerignore, COPY models/ will copy NOTHING!
# So we MUST NOT ignore models/ or data/ or the excel file here.

